parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction of the airbag system, which can lead to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on intermittently
the airbag system appears to malfunction
the airbag warning light stays on
the passenger airbag inflator sensor shows an error
the SRS trouble light comes on and goes off randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbags do not deploy in an accident
the airbag warning light illuminates after an accident
the passenger airbag does not deploy
the driver airbag does not deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag inflator can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of an accident, potentially resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag inflator sensor shows an error
the airbag inflator is malfunctioning
the airbag deploys unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the loss of power steering, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The EPS warning light illuminates
the power steering is lost
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
and the steering system may shut down temporarily.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power inverter can cause the hybrid system to fail, leading to a loss of power and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The IMA/braking/engine/charging/ABS lights illuminate
the car still drives but the hybrid system fails
the 12V battery will not charge and may die
leading to a stall on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rodent damage to electrical wiring can cause various electrical system failures, leading to stalling, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The "check charging system" warning light comes on
the battery drains
the car won't start
the electrical system malfunctions
and the car may stall while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Alternator and battery issues can cause the car to stall or not start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The car won't start
the battery drains
the alternator fails to charge the battery
and the electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag system failure can lead to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
and the system may malfunction or not work properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system malfunctions can cause various issues, including stalling, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The "check charging system" warning light comes on
the electrical system malfunctions
the car may stall while driving
and various other electrical system errors occur.
